{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "律香川奉老伯之命，通过南宫远引荐前往飞鹏古堡求见万鹏王，试图为武老刀的儿子求情，希望万鹏王放走令其心仪的姑娘。万鹏王拒绝接见，但在初一选购古董之日勉强会见律香川。律香川以秦鼎为礼，婉转说明来意，万鹏王以帮规为由断然拒绝。律香川转而观察到万鹏王对一匹汗血宝马极为珍视，心中生出以马要挟的计策。本章展现了律香川的深沉谋略、万鹏王的霸气自信，以及南宫远的消沉颓废。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个男人若为了一个女人而沉迷不能自拔，这人就根本不值得重视，所以你也不必去同情他。",
      "tone": "教诲",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "男人就应该像个男人，说男人的话，做男人的事。",
      "tone": "严厉",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我对人了解得并不多，只知道世上有两种人，一种是仇敌，一种是朋友，做我的朋友，还是仇敌，都由你选择，却绝没有第三种可选的。",
      "tone": "威严",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_nangong_yuan",
      "text": "他不肯？",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nangong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "南宫远",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "他拒绝见你。",
      "tone": "沮丧",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_nangong_yuan",
      "text": "你没提老伯？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nangong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "南宫远",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "他说他和老伯素来没有来往，也不想有什么来往。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_nangong_yuan",
      "text": "你不能要他改变主意？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nangong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "南宫远",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "谁也不能要他改变主意。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nangong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "南宫远",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "每个月初一，是万鹏王选购古董字画的日子。",
      "tone": "提醒",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_nangong_yuan",
      "text": "明天就是初一。",
      "tone": "希望",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nangong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "南宫远",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "光阴似箭，日月如梭，绿鬓少年，忽已白头，人生一梦，梦醒便休，终日碌碌，所为何由？",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_nangong_yuan",
      "text": "也许为的就是此物。",
      "tone": "讥讽",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nangong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "南宫远",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "这是什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_nangong_yuan",
      "text": "五千两银票，这是老伯对你的敬意。",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nangong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "南宫远",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "我这种人还有什么值得尊敬？",
      "tone": "自嘲",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nangong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "南宫远",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人生一梦，梦醒便休，终日碌碌，所为何由。",
      "tone": "悲凉",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_nangong_yuan",
      "text": "我的梦永远不会醒，因为我从没有做过梦。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nangong_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "南宫远",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "但你也知道，每个人偶尔都该做做梦的，是不是？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "古华轩。",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_peng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "万鹏王",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "你是古华轩派来的？",
      "tone": "审视",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_wan_peng_wang",
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "坦率",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_peng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "万鹏王",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "很好，你这人很不简单，能支使你的人当然更不简单。",
      "tone": "赞赏",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_peng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "万鹏王",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "是不是孙玉伯？",
      "tone": "质问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_wan_peng_wang",
      "text": "这就是老伯对帮主的敬意，望帮主笑纳。",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_peng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "万鹏王",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "听说武老刀是从关外流浪到江南的，三十年前才在江南落户生根。",
      "tone": "沉思",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_peng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "万鹏王",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "孙玉伯也是，对不对？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_wan_peng_wang",
      "text": "老伯和武老刀本是一个村子里的人，而且是同时出关的。",
      "tone": "坦诚",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_peng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "万鹏王",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "他要你来替武老刀的儿子求情？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_wan_peng_wang",
      "text": "老伯知道帮主对这种小儿女的私情迟早定会一笑置之，何况，那位姑娘只不过是帮主买来的一个丫头。",
      "tone": "婉转",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_peng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "万鹏王",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "这不是儿女私情的问题，而是本帮的规矩，没有任何人能够破坏本帮的规矩！",
      "tone": "威严",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_wan_peng_wang",
      "text": "老伯素来喜欢朋友，帮主若能与他结交，天下人都必将抚额称庆。",
      "tone": "试探",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_peng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "万鹏王",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "你跟我来！",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_peng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "万鹏王",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "你随便选两样，就算我的回礼。",
      "tone": "豪爽",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_peng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "万鹏王",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "无论什么时候，你若和孙玉伯闹翻了，就到我这里来，我绝不会埋没了你。",
      "tone": "招揽",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_wan_peng_wang",
      "text": "多谢。",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_peng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "万鹏王",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "要不要看看我的马。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_wan_peng_wang",
      "text": "好马，不知是不是大宛的汗血种。",
      "tone": "赞叹",
      "chapter": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_peng_wang",
      "speaker_name": "万鹏王",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "你倒很识货。",
      "tone": "愉快",
      "chapter": 4
    }
  ],
